<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Event Planner Verification</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to Our Platform!</h1>
    <p>Hello <%= eventPlanner %>,</p>
    <p>
      Your account has been created as an event planner (admin) on our platform.
      To activate your account, please click the link below to verify your
      email:
    </p>
    <a href="<%= verificationLink %>">Verify Email</a>
    <p>
      If you did not register as an event planner on our platform, please
      disregard this email.
    </p>
    <p>Best regards,<br />Event Planner Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
